# MMBZalo — Phase 1 Prototype Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A fully working **Phase 1 prototype** from the PLANNING.md spec — focusing on **Authentication & Session Management** with contact parsing capabilities.

### Architecture

```mermaid
graph LR
    A["Dashboard<br/>(HTML/CSS/JS)"] -->|POST /api/validate| B["FastAPI Server<br/>(app/main.py)"]
    A -->|POST /api/parse| B
    B --> C["ZaloDriver<br/>(Playwright)"]
    C -->|Cookie Injection| D["chat.zalo.me<br/>(Headless Chromium)"]
    C -->|DOM Scraping| D
    D -->|Session State| E["auth_state/<br/>session.json"]
```

